[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "……ヴァレリア姉ちゃん、\nこれ、本当に食べていいの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01124",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ええ、もちろん！\nキューンたちのために作ってもらったんだから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01125",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "やったぁ！　ありがとう！\nヤド姉も一緒に食べよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01126",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "諾。感謝する、姉上",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_01127",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "いいのよ、これは二人に時間を作ってもらった\nお礼みたいなものだし。それに――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01128",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "二人の姉として、姉っぽいこと\nしてみたかったのよね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01129",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "えへへ。ありがと、お姉ちゃん！\nロロナのパイ、美味しいな～！　幸せ～！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01130",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "二人とも、喜んでくれてよかった。\n後でロロナにもお礼を言わなくちゃ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01131",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "今度はリーベ姉さんとも一緒に来たいなぁ。\n美味しくて、びっくりするよ！　きっと！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01132",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "食事を楽しむリーベはあまり想像できないけど……\nそうね、今度はリーベも誘いましょ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01133",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……で、今日二人を呼んだのは、\nヘルトの話を聞きたくてなんだけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01134",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "二人から見たヘルトって、どんな奴？\n印象とか、思い出話とかあったら聞かせてほしくて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01135",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "なぜ、ヘルト兄上の話を？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_01136",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ヘルトがどんな人なのかを知ることができれば、\nどうして落ち込んでいるのか分かるかなって思って",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01137",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "そっか。うん、私たちも協力するよ。\nヘルト兄貴がこのままなのは見ていてちょっと辛いし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01138",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "で、ヘルト兄貴の印象と、思い出話かぁ……\nヤド姉はどう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01139",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "ヘルト兄上はとても強い。洗練されている。\n……ゆえに、恐ろしい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_01140",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "私もヤド姉と同じ、かな。\n兄貴に逆らったら、痛いお仕置きされちゃうし……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01141",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そりゃそうよね。\nキューンはブラオールでもそんな感じだったし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01142",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "あ、でも、怖いだけじゃないよ！　昔は、\nたまにだけど、私たちにご飯を作ってくれたりしたし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01143",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "色々作ってくれたんだけど、特訓の後に\n作ってくれたスープが特に美味しいんだよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01144",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "他にも、戦闘の稽古、魔物討伐への同行……\n錬金術の練習に付き合ってくれたこともあった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_01145",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "それ懐かしいね。私たちが錬金術の練習したいって\n言ったら、質のいい素材を集めてきてくれたよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01146",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "へぇ……怖いところもあるけど、\n兄として妹たちの面倒を見ていたのね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01147",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "……でも、やっぱりすっごく厳しかったし、\n調合に失敗したらすっごく怒るから……怖いよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01148",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "調合が上手くいけば、ほめてもらうこともあった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_01149",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "け、けど、やっぱり失敗したらって思うと怖くて、\n怒られないようにヤド姉とこそ練してたなぁ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01150",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ねぇ、ヘルトが調合の練習に付き合ってくれたの？\n調合機能があるのって、私たち三人だけよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01151",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "うん。だけど、ヘルト兄貴は付き合ってくれたよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01152",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "ヘルト兄上はよく言っていた。\n「調合機能を使いこなせるようになれ――」",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_01153",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "「――錬金術の力があれば、もっと強くなれる。\n　それでお前らの存在意義をしっかり示せ」と",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_01154",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（自分に調合機能がないから、\n　機能がある二人に厳しく当たっていたのかしら？）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01155",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（いや、それなら素材を集めてきたりしないし、\n　わざわざ練習に付き合う必要もないわよね）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01156",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（もしかして、ただ兄として\n　二人に成長してほしかった、とか……？）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01157",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "あ！　今日この話をしたこと兄貴には言わないでね！\nお願い！　パイ、少しあげるから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01158",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "姉上、私も",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_01159",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "言わないし、パイはあんたたちが食べなさい。\n私は私で、いっぱい注文してるから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01160",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "二人とも、色々話を聞かせてくれてありがとう。\nすっごく助かったわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01161",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "食べ終わるまで、よかったら二人の話も\n聞かせてくれない？　面白い話がいいな～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01162",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "諾。では視察中、拾った謎の果実を食したために\nキューンの身に起きた悲劇について――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_01163",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ちょっ、ヤド姉！　その話は恥ずかしいからダメー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01164",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]